notes:
Another option:
2. Take it to the Sunbury post office at 135 North Third St; in the lobby area there is a Sunbury-only mail slot.  The slot does not say "ballot drop", but the post office will specially sort out all the ballots dropped at that slot and deliver them immediately to the Elections office.  Any ballots dropped off by 8 pm tomorrow will be counted; those dropped in the Sunbury-only slot today will be delivered tomorrow morning, and those dropped in the Sunbury-only slot tomorrow by 8 pm will be delivered Thursday morning at the latest.
